data.description: Beautiful 2 bedrooms, 2 bath in the city of Sunrise. Townhouse in Red Bridge Community. Centrally located close to many shops, expressways, and restaurants. The backyard has a beautiful patio for entertaining, plenty of parking (3 cars), and right across the street from the community pool. Washer and dryer inside the property. The washer is new. The kitchen was remodeled a year ago. The owner had a recent roof inspection and property inspection. Bring your best buyer because this will not last.
